        <updateDate>2020-04-21T13:18:51Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Tax Returns Unveiled to Secure Transparency Act or the TRUST Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires any candidate for President or Vice President to report their last 10 years of federal income tax returns to the Office of Government Ethics, which the office shall publish on its public website after making the necessary redactions to prevent identity theft or physical danger. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
